105
00:12:45,090 --> 00:12:47,090
Poďte ďalej, sadnite si.

106
00:12:47,090 --> 00:12:50,210
Konečne je tu! Novinár Kim!

107
00:12:50,210 --> 00:12:52,420
Páni, novinár Kim!

108
00:12:52,420 --> 00:12:56,710
